public abstract class SLDExternalGraphic
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISLDFeatures

Implements the ExternalGraphic element of an SLD implementation specification .

The ExternalGraphic element allows a reference to be made to an external graphic file with a Web URL. The onlineResource sub-element gives the URL and the format sub-element identifies the expected document MIME type of a succesful fetch. Knowing the MIME type in advance allows the styler to select the best-supported format from the list of URLs with the equivalent content. Users should avoid referencing external graphics that may change at arbitrary times. Graphic should be static when al all possible.
